{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1719991080.592797", "card_id": "Q_660551862", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 138}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "网传建行总行降薪 10%，子公司的减薪幅度大于总行员工，具体情况如何？银行就业前景如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "7 月 1 日下午，有媒体发布消息，建行将进行大规模的降薪。根据两名知情人士透露，中国建设银行已要求其总部员工减薪至少 10%。其中一位消息人士称，高级官员将大幅度削减工资。另外，建行大多数子公司的减薪幅度大于其总行员工的降薪幅度，但一些表现较好的业务已将减薪幅度限制在个位数。网传建行总行降薪 10%"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-6a67c1548846ca7894f3d7fe0fafaa92_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "679 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660551862"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyJSVk4LnuMRGEAMaCTEwOTA2NzAxNSCQuY+0BjAAOK0DQAByCTY2MDU1MTg2MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1719991080.593793", "card_id": "Q_660599656", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 102}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "赛力斯拟 25 亿元收购问界商标，华为回应「继续帮助车企造好车」，华为为何「剥离」问界商标？如何解读？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "7 月 2 日，赛力斯（601127.SH）公告，公司控股子公司赛力斯汽车有限公司拟收购华为技术有限公司及其关联方持有的已注册或申请中的 919 项问界等系列文字和图形商标，以及 44 项相关外观设计专利，收购价款合计 25 亿元。 证券时报·e 公司消息，对此，华为方面表示，华为将问界等系列商标转让给赛力斯，同时华为将继续支持赛力斯造好问界、卖好问界。华为一贯坚持不造车，而是利用领先的智能网联汽车技术，持续帮助车企造好车、卖好车，华为将继续与车企为用户打造卓越的智能汽车产品，提供极致的智慧出行体验。重磅！赛力斯要花 25 亿元收购「问界」，华为回应 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9e0f3e724068c0d3c30f7bff11a38e17_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "326 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660599656"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyJSVk4LnuMRGEAMaCTEwOTA3NzU1NyCV55K0BjAAOKMBQAFyCTY2MDU5OTY1NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1719991080.594513", "card_id": "Q_660600468", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 51}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "四大一线城市楼市新政效果明显，6 月沪深二手房成交创三年新高，如何解读这一信号？会带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 17 日央行「四箭齐发」助力楼市发展，随后四大一线城市楼市新政全部落地。从市场效果来看，一线城市的房地产市场交易活跃度明显提升。6 月，沪深二手房交易量创下三年来新高；北京二手房网签量创 15 个月新高；广州二手房网签宗数也创下 2023 年 4 月以来的新高。（澎湃新闻）四大一线城市楼市新政效果明显，6 月沪深二手房成交创三年新高 - 中新网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d2b10e6cb8c2145a9e59dfdaa365de9c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "140 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660600468"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyJSVk4LnuMRGEAMaCTEwOTA3NzcyOCCG7ZK0BjAAOGVAAnIJNjYwNjAwNDY4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1719991080.594963", "card_id": "Q_660596513", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "李凯尔先签后换三年 2700 万加盟勇士，该球员有哪些特点？对勇士带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "李凯尔加盟勇士！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e74c7679241fe0e8b8e2afddf068f04c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "114 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660596513"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyJSVk4LnuMRGEAMaCTEwOTA3Njg2OSDYzJK0BjAAOCRAA3IJNjYwNTk2NTEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1719991080.595443", "card_id": "Q_660418298", "card_label": {"type":